Nigerian football federation (NFF) in a tweet congratulated the honorable minister for youth and sports, Mr Sunday Dare as he clocks 54. Happy Birthday to our amiable Honourable Minister for Youth and Sports, Mr. Sunday Dare. Sir, may your birthday be the start of a year filled with good luck, good health, and much happiness. pic.twitter.com/7q2docqNtG The veteran journalist and minister was born May 29, 1966.